<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1002] iPOJO Static binding policy is not compliant with the Declarative Service static binding policy.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1002</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;iPOJO static policy does not stop and start the instance when a static service dependency is broken. The DS specification mentions that the component has to be deactivated, so component instances are lost. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
